  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility package for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial sample omits hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope from the ContextOfUse, leaving the model's range of valid use unspecified (W-ON-02).",
